Spin up a Dask Cluster¶

Since we are using high resolution output, having more computational resources will be helpful

from distributed import Client
from ncar_jobqueue import NCARCluster

cluster = NCARCluster()
cluster.scale(10)
client = Client(cluster)

Open the Dataset¶

ds = xr.open_zarr('../data/monthly_climatology.zarr')

We load in the dataset here to help improve the performance when rendering the plot

ds.load()
